    "### Run Logistic Regression and Gaussian Naive Bayes models on original feature set and Principal Components\n",
    "**PCA improved the performance of the Logistic Regression model!** The highest performing model was the Logisitic Regression model using only the first two principal components.\n",
    "\n",
    "The primary use of PCA in machine learning is to reduce dimensionality and speed up the model, but, as seen below, PCA can also improve model performance by removing collinearity that disrupts the model."
   ]
